wmsLayer.title: GA0305 JB s4 1m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of southern survey area four within Jervis Bay from marine surveys GA0303, GA0305, GA0309 and GA0312, New South Wales. The data is gridded at one metre resolution. A total of eleven areas were surveyed at various resolutions. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 2-60 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/72004.
